=== Cultural properties ===
=== Important Cultural Property (National designation) ===
* {{ill|UNKNOWN|lt=Stone lantern|1=UNKNOWN}} (craft) - the firebox bears the inscription "Enkyō 2辛亥, 4th month, 18th day." Late {{ill|lt=Kamakura period|Q236205|qid=Q236205|1=Kamakura period}}, made in {{ill|lt=Enkyō (Japan)|Q1327068|qid=Q1327068|lt=Enkyō|1=Enkyō (Kamakura period)}} 4 ({{ill|lt=1311|Q5731|qid=Q5731|1=1311}}). Designated on February 2, {{ill|lt=1962|Q2764|qid=Q2764|1=1962}} (Shōwa 37)<ref>{{国指定文化財等データベース|201|6804|Stone lantern}}</ref>.

=== Transportation ===

* From {{ill|lt=Yōkaichi Station|Q8062651|qid=Q8062651|1=Yōkaichi Station}} on the {{ill|lt=Ohmi Railway Main Line|Q7081104|qid=Q7081104|1=Ohmi Railway Main Line}} and {{ill|lt=Ohmi Railway Yōkaichi Line|Q7081107|qid=Q7081107|1=Ohmi Railway Yōkaichi Line}}, take {{ill|lt=Chokotto Bus|Q11271995|qid=Q11271995|1=Chokotto Bus}}, get off at Mikabe Shrine-mae stop, then a short walk.

